          <title>Cale Makar returns from injury, scores twice as Avalanche outlast Wild 9-6 in wacky Game 1</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Cale Makar scored twice in the third period after returning from an earlier injury and the Colorado Avalanche overcame blowing a three-goal lead to beat the Minnesota Wild 9-6 on Sunday night in a wacky Game 1 of their second-round playoff series.]]></description>
